    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is robust, benefiting from a recent VANOS system refresh and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is delivered through a precise six-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing M-spec bushings and MacPherson struts for communicative feedback. This is a mechanically sound machine optimized for performance and tactile engagement.",
