      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved daily driver that remains in impressive mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats are firm and free of punctures, showing only light creasing on the driver-side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the heated seats and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth power, backed by a comprehensive service record that includes a recent fluid flush and brake inspection. The tires have plenty of life left, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This is a smoke-free, pet-free car that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag. It comes with two sets of keys and a clean title.",
